133
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:43,235  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Would you excuse me just a minute?

134
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:47,239  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
I have a surprise for you.
Yes, I do! It's right over here.

135
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:50,996  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
What's that?

136
00:14:57,240 --> 00:15:00,198  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
James. Love always. Della and Felix.

137
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:02,675  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
We love you.

138
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:04,756  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Thanks.

139
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,792  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Come on!

140
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:07,670  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
What the hell's happened?

141
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:11,031  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
How deep is it there?

142
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:13,875  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Call up an amphibian!

143
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:51,677  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Oh, James.
I wanted you to have something.

144
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:56,590  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
You know the tradition? The next one
who catches this is the next one who...

145
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:58,995  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
No. No.

146
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:02,237  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Thanks, Della. It's time I left.

147
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:04,193  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Oh, James.

148
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:15,437  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
- Did I say something wrong?
- He was married once.

149
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:17,915  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
But it was a long time ago.

150
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:26,916  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Felix, you're no good to me
with a wrecked back.

151
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:38,839  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Let her go. I'm the one you want.

152
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:55,477  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
Hey! Ready to go? We got
the batteries recharged on the sub.

153
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:59,593  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:574
